summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 30W, page 91, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Green's Addition, Lot 1 and South 20 ft. of Lot 2, Block 8, and Lot 8, Block 3, located on the northwest and southwest corners of East Boston St. and Eastlake Ave., as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
